&lt;p>The primary use of the Opener is to prepare your cooldown alignment for the rest of the encounter. With our new job design, it’s possible that we’ll actually have fight-specific openers down the stretch.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="standard-opener---no-pt">Standard Opener - No PT&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[344 25 338 129 156 43]" src="https://github.com/RhyTamok/XIVdrg/blob/main/DRG/Graphics/Openers/Dragoon_Standard_Opener_-_No_PT.png?raw=true" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Standard Opener - No PT" />
&lt;/div>

&lt;br>
We use our raidbuff Battle Litany after applying our DoT for party alignment, the rest of our buffs surround it with Geirskogul being used last to ensure its own potency is buffed by all our personal buffs and potential raidbuffs.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Dragoon FAQ</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/faq/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:37:28 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/faq/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Type &lt;code>!faq drg&lt;/code> in #bot_spam for a full list of commands to answer other common questions!&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;em>How does Raiden Thrust work?&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>Raiden Thrust is an upgraded True Thrust. It combos into both Disembowel and Vorpal Thrust and replaces True Thrust on your bar when it’s ready. You activate it by successfully landing the positional on the fifth hit of your combo (Fang and Claw or Wheeling Thrust following Wheeling Thrust or Fang and Claw, respectively). If you fail, you get to press True Thrust and hear a laugh track play in the background.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Dragoon Best in Slot (BiS)</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/best-in-slot/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:24:31 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/best-in-slot/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Stat Priority</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/stat-priority/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:23:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/stat-priority/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Changes</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/job-changes/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:21:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/job-changes/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dragoon Advanced Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/advanced-guide/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Sep 2022 20:41:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/advanced-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p>Due to the nature of the Dragoon job design, advanced content is included and covered within the &lt;a href="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/dragoon/basic-guide/">Basic Guide&lt;/a>. If you have further questions regarding DRG optimization, please feel free to ask in the Discord server.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>